{"tid":2185123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得部分連登仔有需要糾正理解\"台灣\"既觀念?","createTime":"2020-09-02T05:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T21:24:57.000Z","uid":212731,"like":92,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e9e7a97a966c5cf9088277d7a46dc363040a50","tid":2185123,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"部分連登仔喺理解&quot;台灣&quot;上 仍然抱有好大中華膠既思維<br />\n未意識到台灣既方向一直都係以建構&quot;台灣國族&quot;為核心而行<br />\n<br />\n正確既思路應該係咁:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中華民國... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正名台灣國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反攻大陸，統一中華... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />守護台灣人民同台灣國土<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中華正統在台灣...  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />台灣文化就係台灣文化，由閩南、日本、原住民、歐美等文化數百年融合演變而形成，係獨立而存既文化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Taiwanese is the real chinese!... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />chinese還chinese，Taiwanese還Taiwanese，唔好搞錯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港其實要回歸中華民國... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港台關係應該同台日關係一樣，係可以獨立平等地交流"},{"pid":"3aeac4d8c40705d08f896748d1642a3f5611275d","tid":2185123,"uid":212731,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"即刻兩個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1dbf87d2a23c6d13298cbe6927495ee1a051a8f","tid":2185123,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T05:10:51.000Z","msg":"方向一直都係(憲法仲係中華民國)"},{"pid":"98095b3258a667067bc4d7943ec74d681ac7da15","tid":2185123,"uid":212731,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a1dbf87d2a23c6d13298cbe6927